WEBVTT

1
00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:08.800
Goddamn thing

2
00:00:08.966 --> 00:00:10.766
How dare you cheat

3
00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:14.366
Are you worthy of the years of hard work?

4
00:00:14.466 --> 00:00:16.100
Who is that woman?

5
00:00:16.966 --> 00:00:19.966
Grandpa's rice can be eaten indiscriminately

6
00:00:19.966 --> 00:00:21.233
Talk nonsense

7
00:00:21.466 --> 00:00:22.866
There are no women outside

8
00:00:22.866 --> 00:00:26.000
Why did you divorce Master Jing? Why?

9
00:00:27.533 --> 00:00:29.600
Do I need a reason to divorce you?

10
00:00:29.700 --> 00:00:33.266
I have seen all the efforts I have made this year

11
00:00:34.166 --> 00:00:36.066
Leave if you say so

12
00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:38.966
Do you have an old man like me in your eyes?

13
00:00:39.700 --> 00:00:42.066
I only know this one granddaughter-in-law

14
00:00:42.666 --> 00:00:44.566
I don't interfere with your thoughts

15
00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:47.100
Anyway, I am not the only grandson of yours.

16
00:00:47.100 --> 00:00:48.933
What nonsense are you talking about?

17
00:00:48.933 --> 00:00:50.933
There is my old man on this day

18
00:00:50.933 --> 00:00:52.966
I will not allow you two to divorce

19
00:00:54.966 --> 00:00:56.433
It's not up to you to say it

20
00:00:57.133 --> 00:00:58.266
It's what I say

21
00:01:00.566 --> 00:01:03.233
I don't have patience

22
00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:06.966
Forestry even dares to ignore the old man's words

23
00:01:07.100 --> 00:01:08.833
With his vigorous means

24
00:01:08.966 --> 00:01:11.466
If I don't sign, there will definitely be no good fruit to eat

25
00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:13.666
OK, I'll sign.

26
00:01:14.266 --> 00:01:15.766
I don't ask for anything else.

27
00:01:15.933 --> 00:01:17.566
I just hope you treat Jing Rui well.

